reviewText: Purchased this for the 3 year old grandson and he is quite enamored.  He watches it all the time.
I was under the impression this was a new bubble guppies dvd but it was just a collection of the old ones we already have. He was very disappointed.

This is actually just a repackaging of two previously released DVDs! Both DVDs were already released & all this is is just a new cardboard sleeve that the two DVDs are now sold together in. Very disappointing!

First off this is a DVD set of two Bubble Guppies DVDs:  Bubble Guppies and Bubble Guppies On the Job!  So if you already have those two DVDs the you definitely don't need this one.  If you don't own those two Bubble Guppies DVDs then this would be a great set for any fan.  It features 230 minutes of Bubble Guppies, which is a whole lot of those swimming silly friends.  The friends are wholesome and teach great values for kids.

"On the Job" Episodes:

Fishketball!
A Tooth on the Looth!
Build Me a Building!
The Grumpfish Special!
Call a Clambulance!
Firefighter Gil to the Rescue!
"Bubble Guppies" Episodes:

Bubble Puppys Fin-Tastic Fairy Tale! (Double-Length Episode)
Bubble Puppy
Bubble Bites

Thought I was getting my 2 year old some new episodes that he didn't have yet but turns out we have both of the DVDs.  The cover of this pack makes it seem like it's a new twin pack dvd set but really isn't.  Disappointed and feel deceived by the new cover.  Description should say what DVDs are inside this pack.
Read discription before buying! I was under the impression I was buying a new bubble guppies DVD! But it's two older DVDs in one package :( real disappointed with this.

I thought this was new episodes of the guppies turns out it's just the first two dvds together in new packaging.  Big disappointment for my little guppies fan.  Love the guppies wish they were new episodes out

When this item game up for pre-order, I assumed it was a new collection of Bubble Guppies cartoons that had not yet been released on DVD. Unfortunately, it is only a repackaging of two DVD's that were previously released individually - Bubble Guppies & Bubble Guppies: On The Job.

I've rated it 3 stars only because the description was not clear on the contents. My daughter loved the DVDs when we originally purchased them, so if you do not already have those, this is a good deal.

I have posted a picture of the backside of the dvds, which I believe should be included in the item pictures above.
